Subject: Re: [T2] oil temp

On 4/2/06 8:43 AM, "Kevin H. Roberts" <bopsax(-at-)yahoo.com> wrote:

> Hi guys and gals.  I'm considering tapping out my oil drain plug  and putting
> the temp sender from BD in it.  Has anyone had trouble  with them leaking?  I
> haven't found anybody to do it so I'll  probably have to try it myself.  I'll
> need a 14mm drill bit and a  14 x 1.5 tap.

You need a 12.5mm drill bit. To calculate the drill size for a metric
thread, subtract the pitch from the thread size.

14mm thread - 1.5 pitch = 12.5mm pilot drill size.


